    {
      "id": "5ad5c697_d9505802",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "message": "This isn't quite ready.  I submitted it as a WIP so that I could see a gating run.  I need to release the drprov-client image, and I also need to change the readiness checks for pm-mapper and datafile-collector, which are currently waiting for a job that runs after bus controller is deployed.   The 5G bulk pm test exercises the DR (the datafile-collector publishes a file to a DR feed, and the pm-mapper subscribes to that feed and receives the file)--that test is working in my local environment and also in gating.  In my local environment it's possible to see the feed and the subscription that are being created (a query to the DR API shows them) and it's also possible to see the file being published and delivered by looking at the DR logs after the 5G bulk PM test runs.",
      "author": {
